text: Rainer Holzhaider (born 2 August 1956) is an Austrian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Austria Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Gmunden Category:Sportspeople from Upper Austria
